background with AV foundation

00:28:42.396 --> 00:28:44.656 A:middle
APIs, media remote commands and

00:28:44.736 --> 00:28:46.106 A:middle
access to now playing info.

00:28:47.466 --> 00:28:48.746 A:middle
You can make your fitness apps

00:28:48.746 --> 00:28:50.256 A:middle
more robust and reliable with

00:28:50.256 --> 00:28:51.576 A:middle
the new workout builder API.

00:28:52.966 --> 00:28:54.506 A:middle
And you can provide value on the

00:28:54.506 --> 00:28:56.306 A:middle
Siri Watch face by creating

00:28:56.306 --> 00:28:57.276 A:middle
relevant shortcuts.

